#date:04.02.2026 task-61. What is Bitcoin â€” Definition
Bitcoin is the first decentralized digital currency that allows people to send value directly to each other over the internet without intermediaries (like banks or governments).
It runs on a technology called blockchain, which keeps a public, tamper-proof record of all transactions. ğŸª™
